---
title: HITL 确认流程时序图
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    actorTextColor: "#1a1a1a"
    fontSize: 13
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 用户
    participant Browser as 🌐 Browser
    participant Express as Express :3000
    participant Confirm as confirm-state
    participant Tool as 插件 Tool
    participant API as 插件 API

    Note over Tool,Confirm: Tool 执行时调用 requestConfirm()
    
    Tool->>Confirm: requestConfirm(toolName, formData)
    Note over Confirm: Promise 挂起 ⏳<br/>等待用户决策
    
    Confirm-->>Express: getPending() ≠ null
    Express-->>Browser: SSE: confirm_required<br/>{ tool, label, form, fieldLabels }
    Browser-->>User: 弹出确认卡片<br/>📋 确认提交表单
    
    alt 用户确认
        User->>Browser: 点击 ✅ 确认
        Browser->>Express: POST /api/confirm<br/>{ approved: true }
        Express->>Confirm: approveConfirm()
        Confirm-->>Tool: Promise resolve(true)
        Tool->>API: submitApi(form) / startProcessApi(...)
        API-->>Tool: 返回结果
        Tool-->>Express: 返回 tool 结果
        Express-->>Browser: SSE: confirm_resolved + tool_result
        Browser-->>User: 显示成功消息
    else 用户拒绝
        User->>Browser: 点击 ❌ 拒绝
        Browser->>Express: POST /api/confirm<br/>{ approved: false }
        Express->>Confirm: rejectConfirm()
        Confirm-->>Tool: Promise resolve(false)
        Tool-->>Express: throw Error("用户拒绝")
        Express-->>Browser: SSE: confirm_resolved + tool_result
        Browser-->>User: 显示拒绝消息，Agent 重新收集
    end